cating the brief context**\\n\\nI need to clarify what the brief is. Maybe there's context in the files I can check. I'll look into the workspace first to see if there's a specific request there. It seems I can inspect memory too, which might help. Since I'm acting as a subagent, I should follow the instructions provided and read both SOUL and USER memory from today. Let's get started locating those files!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_HaMR0NgqNUt8bgKFBP2GKtZf|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f67448194a9270b681ee2167f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -ლა","workdir":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"ls -ლა\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0sqSmkXvThqIngSe0rtVwOTK|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f675c819488a8daf397b5762d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find . -maxdepth 3 -type f -name \"*dieline*\" -o -name \"*.svg\" | sed 's|^./||' | head","workdir":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find . -maxdepth 3 -type f -name \\\"*dieline*\\\" -o -name \\\"*.svg\\\" | sed 's|^./||' | head\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_rN07pVDUwtAiaHHVZs2zbwua|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f67648194b715d8284e3715dd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -1","workdir":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"ls -1\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_o7Ub2Jba9p0OnrOo1FGdKOW5|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f677081949d22be3af04521bd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/SOUL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/SOUL.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vgdIMj6plAGLNvOivEaWZqWH|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f67788194bee232a2282cbbab","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/USER.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director/USER.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6U9OeEEDywJWfbz8FYH9mdtn|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f678081948d2558502e96e53c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"date","workdir":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"date\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.2","usage":{"input":4276,"output":309,"cacheRead":1408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":5993,"cost":{"input":0.007483,"output":0.004326,"cacheRead":0.00024639999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0120554}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771379545014}}
{"type":"message","id":"e17c4781","parentId":"03728a0f","timestamp":"2026-02-18T01:52:31.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_HaMR0NgqNUt8bgKFBP2GKtZf|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b5f67448194a9270b681ee2167f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"exec\",\n  \"error\": \"ls: invalid option -- �\\nusage: ls [-@ABCFGHILOPRSTUWXabcdefghiklmnopqrstuvwxy1%,] [--color=when] [-D format] [file ...]\\n\\nCommand exited with code 1\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"exec","error":"ls: invalid option -- �\nusage: ls [-@ABCFGHILOPRSTUWXabcdefghiklmnopqrstuvwxy1%,] [--color=when] [-D format] [file ...]\n\nCommand exited with code 1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771379551995}}
