{"type":"message","id":"1d8e51ce","parentId":"091a2efd","timestamp":"2026-02-18T01:52:38.526Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4DV4nIjto3EIw0sgwYBdk7Q5|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b65ed5881949c442a7d1c8792d9","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"designers\ninfluences"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"designers\ninfluences","cwd":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771379558524}}
{"type":"message","id":"c219a105","parentId":"1d8e51ce","timestamp":"2026-02-18T01:52:38.530Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_DYqw2ctxaiQoC8iapIPvRMj8|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b65ed6081948668d7713cdab230","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TCR Creative Loop (Zara-led)\n\nGoal: keep Producer/Copy/Design/Growth in a tight feedback loop with Zara as taste gate.\n\n## 3× Daily Learning Loops (minimum)\nEach loop is **10 minutes**:\n1) **Ship/Show:** each agent posts 1 artifact (draft, image, hook list, layout, angle)\n2) **Zara gate:** Zara replies with `SHIP / REVISE / KILL` + 1–2 line why\n3) **Rule extraction:** if a pattern repeats, promote to a rule\n4) **Proof:** link the artifact + note what changed\n\n## Required proof\nEvery improvement must include:\n- Before/after (or v1/v2)\n- What rule changed\n- What metric/heuristic improved\n\n## Output format (per agent)\n- Artifact link/path:\n- Zara verdict:\n- Change made:\n- Proof (before/after):\n- New rule (if any):\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771379558528}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f7fdcb2","parentId":"c219a105","timestamp":"2026-02-18T01:53:03.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, it looks like I'm not finding any SVG files. Maybe I need to dig a bit deeper. There seems to be an issue with the search not outputting results, possibly due to the order of parentheses in my query. I think I should locate the problem and troubleshoot from there. Let's see how I can refine my search to get the desired output!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b7c136881949e452daee6169943\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABplRt_XDkxfqVWy-3_QwifHMFfKP0JkSWaRPhbUprF7LgqBD_VOo5BkiOg3imJkXJ9qTkWGzGNiXwwMN51b42LhOZAbEjPSKc-lnR3si7BqyLbfEdE1-rWLBha4gRpdVEsPqLv9Amsh8X0QpLZwKMnkZW6kCTX5GqzFpxlrqyk1ylYicIMjl2AYtb_dgtQAo63o6wYNViu1-J1yW-7VmZFhYhoDXPUZRckgqv-1aC3AxawHdTRCFDeV2CQUZTRMamaYhWyDIChg3_d1-Ko2yWGyqICsd93_xHf193aP-HafPr29rchpXqUL7f0nRfYwpTUjDbbgkDk71dT1270QzPaj_daS_4y4OTNy18xHXC2KoJV5T4rAFjLaiaOk-dFJajmq-hGZjmW9d0VX1clNsFFmTaBwkzT5wJPx1rDCK0N6AjCH_ABFWliF6e8H2gyyy52kA722OVsbF3X8tDcmb_fgnUwMxhWyeHJrT8spgIM-4PMnffYmmDn060b3ZE0GM6NZ2RS-AiNnmxlyZoTJO8Tl0tSlmLha7q_sN9fo2Y1kDhzmkmHG3oDBsznh7wc5tstRkufKor6kA6m95h4_KlQwn3C6qQeuC4O0fG3lMlbBFbc3hQPXuxgRCO4fwZiuvjDHcqrfHLT7Qz7mhP8Re78quRIzhbh0NXMislBgEf_RvXzxtZF1TGcIzaQvUmBXjg8JSgezIKRmUmQ4aPJmXHMT44iVLImIMfjwPmjKwb2Dgpu__wRNeZ56dv36GJJeA0mOHFH_9-IGloAUjKVhG87AygR6iitokE1y4hWY87mS-MDNVxE5a3F2ooAEvnGlH3TTHbnBRJOrfd3CR4J0jNAnXzhZwuhO0bOs1GDWvDyaIBJJe1UFSGDjkMkjF6Qkp_UomiOPDjVYqeQTykYmvGdvquc-IDi9XhZ0AdkPWIyqAoO4Xk_wizZGFUBx17OMbNjUS4V6u7kU8M5X_mxSg0skqhQXw==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"Hmm, it looks like I'm not finding any SVG files. Maybe I need to dig a bit deeper. There seems to be an issue with the search not outputting results, possibly due to the order of parentheses in my query. I think I should locate the problem and troubleshoot from there. Let's see how I can refine my search to get the desired output!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ZaqFwgrdRq0iMiHKgW2rvSAU|fc_09467bfd90a6e5210169951b7f125c8194ac96febab77bc329","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find . -type f -name \"*.svg\" | sed 's|^./||' | head -n 50","workdir":"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find . -type f -name \\\"*.svg\\\" | sed 's|^./||' | head -n 50\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/calbotsman/.openclaw/workspace-director\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.2","usage":{"input":8525,"output":85,"cacheRead":1408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10018,"cost":{"input":0.01491875,"output":0.00119,"cacheRead":0.00024639999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01635515}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771379558530}}
